title: Black Tower - Inerya - dark electro industrial ebm goth gothic
description:
Released: 2014
Label: Halotan Records
Style: dark electro, industrial, ebm, aggrotech, goth, gothic, darkwave
More info: www.halotan.net

Interya contains 50 minutes of atmospheric dark electronic music. The style can be defined as mixture of electro industrial and darkwave. Especially the vocals tend to lean towards more lyrical side of dark independent scene.

Having said this one can't deny that at least a couple of songs have strong dancefloor potential and would easily keep people moving during any dark alternative party.
